<p>But the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit model has plenty to keep her entertained, as she prepares to welcome baby number three.</p>

<p>She got quite the laugh out of a very graphic placenta cake Friday, as she took to her Instagram Story to show off the thoughtful dessert she received from friend and makeup artist Kristine Studden.</p>

