<p>The 34-year-old could be heard laughing in the background of the video, as she exclaimed: 'Oh my god! Oh my god, thank you Kristine. This is so disgusting!'</p>

<p>'Who's gonna eat this?' husband John Legend, 41, asked, to which she passionately responded: 'Me! I'm going to... Oh my god, the cord.'</p>

