<p>Chrissy later posted another video to her Insta Story, giving a glimpse of a compression device wrapped around her leg, during bed rest.</p>

<p>She explained: 'A lot of you got a glimpse of these guys. It is like a little machine that compresses your legs. You get it when you're on bed rest or when you're in the hospital, so you don't get blood clots.</p>

<p>'Because that's what happens when you lay down for too long, and it can be really dangerous. So, I have these on for a few weeks.'</p>

<p>The topic of blood clots apparently carried on into a private group chat after that post, as she revealed she accidentally sent a very graphic photo to the wrong chat.</p>

<p>The Lip Sync Battle host checked in once again, this time using a dog face filter, telling her 31.3million followers: 'I just sent the most disgusting photo to the group chat of a blood clot that I like caught... from my pee.</p>

<p>'It was huge. I don't know if it's a clot, I don't know what the hell it is. It's like a giant ball, a bloody ball. And I posted it in the group chat, but it was the wrong group chat.'</p>

